{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":666,"text":"When I opened Mott Hall\nBridges Academy in 2010,"},{"time":6037,"text":"my goal was simple:"},{"time":8555,"text":"open a school to close a prison."},{"time":12525,"text":"Now to some, this was an audacious goal,"},{"time":15534,"text":"because our school is located\nin the Brownsville section of Brooklyn --"},{"time":19773,"text":"one of the most underserved\nand violent neighborhoods"},{"time":22997,"text":"in all of New York City."},{"time":26121,"text":"Like many urban schools\nwith high poverty rates,"},{"time":30427,"text":"we face numerous challenges,"},{"time":33173,"text":"like finding teachers who can empathize"},{"time":35623,"text":"with the complexities\nof a disadvantaged community,"},{"time":40054,"text":"lack of funding for technology,"},{"time":42675,"text":"low parental involvement"},{"time":45433,"text":"and neighborhood gangs that recruit\nchildren as early as fourth grade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52886,"text":"So here I was,"},{"time":55416,"text":"the founding principal of a middle school\nthat was a district public school,"},{"time":61728,"text":"and I only had 45 kids to start."},{"time":66024,"text":"Thirty percent of them had special needs."},{"time":69797,"text":"Eighty-six percent of them\nwere below grade level"},{"time":72862,"text":"in English and in math."},{"time":75701,"text":"And 100 percent were living\nbelow the poverty level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81258,"text":"If our children are not in our classrooms,"},{"time":84591,"text":"how will they learn?"},{"time":86731,"text":"And if they're not learning,"},{"time":88529,"text":"where would they end up?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91402,"text":"It was evident when I would\nask my 13-year-old,"},{"time":96396,"text":"\"Young man,"},{"time":97681,"text":"where do you see yourself in five years?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":101663,"text":"And his response:"},{"time":103691,"text":"\"I don't know if I'm gonna\nlive that long.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":106971,"text":"Or to have a young woman say to me"},{"time":111252,"text":"that she had a lifelong goal\nof working in a fast-food restaurant."},{"time":116800,"text":"To me, this was unacceptable."},{"time":119862,"text":"It was also evident that they had no idea"},{"time":123123,"text":"that there was a landscape of opportunity"},{"time":125292,"text":"that existed beyond their neighborhood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129055,"text":"We call our students \"scholars,\"\nbecause they're lifelong learners."},{"time":134597,"text":"And the skills that they learn today"},{"time":136401,"text":"will prepare them for college\nand career readiness."},{"time":140931,"text":"I chose the royal colors\nof purple and black,"},{"time":145786,"text":"because I want them to be reminded\nthat they are descendants of greatness,"},{"time":150584,"text":"and that through education,"},{"time":152433,"text":"they are future engineers,"},{"time":154504,"text":"scientists,"},{"time":155690,"text":"entrepreneurs"},{"time":157077,"text":"and even leaders who can and will\ntake over this world."},{"time":162544,"text":"To date,"},{"time":163846,"text":"we have had three graduating classes,"},{"time":167959,"text":"at a 98 --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":169369,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178341,"text":"At a 98-percent graduation rate."},{"time":182120,"text":"This is nearly 200 children,"},{"time":184977,"text":"who are now going to some of the most\ncompetitive high schools"},{"time":188257,"text":"in New York City."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189755,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":197675,"text":"It was a cold day in January"},{"time":200872,"text":"when my scholar, Vidal Chastanet,\nmet Brandon Stanton,"},{"time":205462,"text":"the founder of the popular blog\n\"Humans of New York.\""},{"time":210102,"text":"Brandon shared the story\nof a young man from Brownsville"},{"time":214019,"text":"who had witnessed violence firsthand,"},{"time":217977,"text":"by witnessing a man\nbeing thrown off of a roof."},{"time":222264,"text":"Yet he can still\nbe influenced by a principal"},{"time":225727,"text":"who had opened up a school\nthat believes in all children."},{"time":230490,"text":"Vidal embodies the story of so many\nof our underprivileged children"},{"time":236119,"text":"who are struggling to survive,"},{"time":238859,"text":"which is why we must\nmake education a priority."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243992,"text":"Brandon's post created a global sensation"},{"time":247228,"text":"that touched the lives of millions."},{"time":250855,"text":"This resulted in 1.4 million\ndollars being raised"},{"time":255390,"text":"for our scholars to attend field trips\nto colleges and universities,"},{"time":262001,"text":"Summer STEAM programs,"},{"time":264303,"text":"as well as college scholarships."},{"time":267792,"text":"You need to understand"},{"time":268993,"text":"that when 200 young people\nfrom Brownsville visited Harvard,"},{"time":275308,"text":"they now understood"},{"time":277161,"text":"that a college of their choice\nwas a real possibility."},{"time":282457,"text":"And the impossibilities\nthat had been imposed upon them"},{"time":286431,"text":"by a disadvantaged community"},{"time":288585,"text":"were replaced by hope and purpose."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293498,"text":"The revolution in education\nis happening in our schools,"},{"time":299349,"text":"with adults who provide love,"},{"time":302727,"text":"structure,"},{"time":303927,"text":"support"},{"time":305113,"text":"and knowledge."},{"time":306963,"text":"These are the things\nthat inspire children."},{"time":310806,"text":"But it is not an easy task."},{"time":313815,"text":"And there are high demands"},{"time":316709,"text":"within an education system\nthat is not perfect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320893,"text":"But I have a dynamic group of educators"},{"time":324756,"text":"who collaborate as a team to determine\nwhat is the best curriculum."},{"time":329553,"text":"They take time beyond their school day,"},{"time":332447,"text":"and come in on weekends"},{"time":333768,"text":"and even use their own money\nto often provide resources"},{"time":338921,"text":"when we do not have it."},{"time":341804,"text":"And as the principal,"},{"time":343676,"text":"I have to inspect what I expect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347308,"text":"So I show up in classes"},{"time":349836,"text":"and I conduct observations\nto give feedback,"},{"time":352946,"text":"because I want my teachers\nto be just as successful"},{"time":356385,"text":"as the name Mott Hall Bridges Academy."},{"time":359930,"text":"And I give them access to me\nevery single day,"},{"time":363646,"text":"which is why they all have\nmy personal cell number,"},{"time":366534,"text":"including my scholars\nand those who graduated --"},{"time":369616,"text":"which is probably why I get\nphone calls and text messages"},{"time":372598,"text":"at three o'clock in the morning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374386,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":376174,"text":"But we are all connected to succeed,"},{"time":378794,"text":"and good leaders do this."},{"time":382282,"text":"Tomorrow's future is sitting\nin our classrooms."},{"time":386304,"text":"And they are our responsibility."},{"time":389526,"text":"That means everyone in here,"},{"time":391527,"text":"and those who are watching the screen."},{"time":394649,"text":"We must believe in their brilliance,"},{"time":398234,"text":"and remind them by teaching them"},{"time":400867,"text":"that there indeed is power in education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406047,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407251,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}